When American scientists are kidnapped by a foreign power, Thor rushes over international borders to save them! But how will the Thunder God respond when the scientists are held hostage, and he knows all his power may not be enough to save them? Meanwhile, Jane Foster decides she loves Thor, not Donald Blake! But aren't they the same man?
